personal.name: Kaelen Jennings
personal.title: Business Problem Solver & Full Stack Developer

bio.short: I build systems that solve real business problems. Full-stack developer specializing in AI-powered automation, workflow optimization, and industry-specific applications that directly impact your bottom line.
long: I don't just write code - I solve business problems. My focus is identifying pain points in your operations and building custom systems that eliminate inefficiencies, automate repetitive tasks, and unlock new revenue opportunities.

My approach starts with understanding your business needs, not the technology. Whether it's reducing administrative overhead by 60% with AI-powered CRMs, creating automated business intelligence systems, or building industry-specific applications, I deliver solutions that show measurable ROI.

I've successfully built systems for real estate professionals, fitness industries, and business development teams. Each project demonstrates my ability to combine technical expertise with deep business understanding to create tools that actually solve problems.

taglines: I Build Systems That Solve Real Business Problems
Turn Manual Processes Into Automated Systems
AI-Powered Solutions That Show Measurable ROI
